OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers in
OL,6,Fthe south fading, as the cloudy
OL,7,Fconditions in the north extend
OL,8,Fsouthwards, with hill fog and the odd
OL,9,Fspot of drizzle. Light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CMonday:FGradually turning brighter
OL,12,Ffrom the north and mostly dry,
OL,13,Falthough a few light showers are still
OL,14,Fpossible. Winds remaining generally
OL,15,Flight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
